rs infuses capital and applies our operating expertise to grow those brands we look at franchise companies not just as financial investments but as living entities in which concept foundersmanagement and franchisees have invested substantial amounts of time and resources our goal is to use our operational and financial experience to position high quality brands for accelerated but responsible growth our management our team has extensive franchise experience spanning single store operations to public companies at our core we are operators collectively our team has been involved with  brands including top global companies like popeyes burger king subway and dominos we’ve also worked with major regional brands such as moes southwest grill pet valu super wash and local startups like urban grounds and tutor force our experience encompasses every area of the franchise business model from sales financing and real estate development to operations marketing hr technology and successful exit strategies our motivation our fund was born when our founder aziz hashim set out to fulfill two goals  to put  entrepreneurs into business and  to provide our franchiseeinvestors with an opportunity to participate in business as franchisors the core pillar of nrds strategy is to invest in brands where franchisee success is the central value  of  investment proﬁle sectors sectors we invest in franchisors segments of particular interest include restaurants all formats wellness and beauty education and healthcare however brands with exceptional productsservices and strong unit economics regardless of sector are always of interest stage stage we seek brands that have achieved proof of concept delineators include superior unit economics geographic diversity and franchisee success size size our fund seeks to make equity investments from mm up to mm portfolio brand experience portfolio our team susan e beth chief operating officer aziz hashim managing partner shawn lederman director richard pawl